---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Pink Payroll Guarantee — Accuracy. On Time. Every Time." description="Pink Payroll backs every payroll run with our accuracy and on-time guarantee. If we make a mistake, we fix it and cover any resulting penalties — no excuses.">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-5">Our Promise to You</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight max-w-3xl">
        The Pink Payroll<br class="hidden md:block" />
        <span class="text-pink">Guarantee.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        After 18 years processing payroll for California small businesses, we've built our reputation on one principle: if we touch it, we own it. Accuracy. On time. Every payroll run.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== THE THREE PILLARS ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">What We Back</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Three Commitments. Zero Asterisks.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        These aren't marketing bullet points — they are the operating standards every Pink Payroll client gets, starting on day one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <div class="border-l-4 border-pink bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">100% Accuracy</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          Every paycheck, every withholding, every tax deposit — calculated correctly. If a Pink Payroll processing error causes a penalty or interest charge from a tax authority, we cover it. Not you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-pink bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">On-Time Delivery</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          Your employees get paid on the date they expect — every single time. We process on schedule and manage the deadlines so you never have to worry about a missed payroll again.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-[#C62028] bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#C62028]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#C62028]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">Real Human Support</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          When something needs to be resolved, you reach a real person who knows your account — not a support ticket number. We respond and resolve, not deflect and delay.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== PENALTY PROTECTION ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-gray/40 border-y border-brand-light-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Penalty Protection</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-6">
            Our Error. <span class="text-pink">Our Bill.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
            If a penalty or interest charge is assessed by the IRS, EDD, or any state or local tax authority because of a Pink Payroll processing error, we will pay it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-5">
            This isn't a "we'll try our best" promise — it's how we've operated for 18 years. Our team has the depth of California expertise to get it right the first time and stand behind the work when it matters.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-gray/70 leading-relaxed">
            Penalty protection applies to errors originating from Pink Payroll's processing. Penalties resulting from client-supplied incorrect data, late submissions to our office, or changes outside our system are handled on a case-by-case basis with our support team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          {[
            { icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z', label: 'IRS & Federal Tax Penalties' },
            { icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z', label: 'California EDD Penalties' },
            { icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z', label: 'State & Local Tax Agency Notices' },
            { icon: 'M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z', label: 'Interest Charges from Late Deposits' },
          ].map(({ icon, label }) => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl px-6 py-4 shadow-sm">
              <span class="w-9 h-9 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-pink/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={icon}/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <p class="font-semibold text-brand-black text-sm">{label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== HOW TO CLAIM ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">If Something Goes Wrong</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">How to Activate the Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        No forms, no claims department, no waiting. Here is how it works.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {[
        {
          step: '01',
          title: 'Contact Your Team',
          body: 'Call or message your dedicated Pink Payroll contact directly. Describe the notice or discrepancy and share any documentation you received.',
        },
        {
          step: '02',
          title: 'We Review & Own It',
          body: 'Our team reviews the issue immediately. If the error originated from our processing, we take responsibility — no deflecting, no blame-shifting.',
        },
        {
          step: '03',
          title: 'We Resolve & Cover',
          body: 'We correct the error, communicate with the agency on your behalf where applicable, and cover any penalties or interest charges that resulted from our mistake.',
        },
      ].map(({ step, title, body }) => (
        <div class="text-center px-6 py-10 bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-light-gray mb-4">{step}</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">{title}</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed text-sm">{body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHY WE CAN BACK THIS ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Foundation</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">
            Why We Can Stand<br />
            <span class="text-pink">Behind This Promise.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Most payroll companies offer a guarantee because it looks good on paper. We offer ours because 18 years of California-focused expertise has made it a safe promise to keep.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Our team processes payroll under some of the most complex labor and tax environments in the country. California's requirements are a different league from the rest of the U.S. — and we've built every system, every check, and every workflow around getting them right.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          {[
            { stat: '18+', label: 'Years of California Payroll Expertise' },
            { stat: '5.0★', label: 'Average Rating on Google & Yelp' },
            { stat: '50', label: 'U.S. States Supported' },
            { stat: '100%', label: 'U.S.-Based Team & Support' },
          ].map(({ stat, label }) => (
            <div class="border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-pink mb-2">{stat}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs leading-snug">{label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== GUARANTEE TERMS & LIMITATIONS ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Guarantee Terms and Limitations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">I. Guarantee Nullification for Insufficient Funds</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          This Satisfaction Guarantee is expressly contingent upon the timely and full funding of all payrolls and tax liabilities during the introductory 90-day period. In the event that a client's bank account incurs a Non-Sufficient Funds (NSF) notification, return, or failure for any payroll transaction processed by Pink Payroll, this guarantee shall be deemed null, void, and unenforceable by the client. The occurrence of a single NSF event, regardless of cure, forfeits all rights to a refund under this offer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">II. Limit of Refundable Fees</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Only the specifically enumerated Base Fees and Per Check Fees directly associated with processing are subject to a refund under this guarantee. All other service and ancillary fees are explicitly excluded from this offer.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-black mb-3">Non-Refundable Costs include, but are not limited to:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {[
            'Timekeeping and attendance software or service fees.',
            'Shipping and delivery charges (e.g., expedited check delivery).',
            'New employee charges or onboarding fees.',
            'Account setup and implementation fees.',
            'Hardware purchase or rental charges.',
            'Government-imposed penalties, interest, or fines.',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-gray/40 inline-block"></span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FINAL CTA ===== -->
  <section class="bg-pink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Ready to Run Payroll Without the Worry?</h2>
      <p class="text-pink-light text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Let's talk about your payroll setup and show you exactly what the guarantee covers for your business.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://link.pinkpayroll.com/widget/booking/gZIYVYUm3txLBKTRjTZd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white text-pink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base">
          Schedule a Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white/60 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-base">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
